name: almost palm trees
description:
if the light were good, the film were clean, the cam were working and the birds were singing, maybe we would have gotten something out of this shot, maybe we would have seen these folks lovingly strolling down the sandy road, upbeat with their shirts off and their smile on.

but avec des si, on pourrait mettre paris en bouteille, and maybe with the right wind, the right waves and the right will, the bottle would have come right there, in Kauai, by these blurry almost palm trees.

who knows
